1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"wmullins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1310:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">UpdraftPlus are pleased to announce that we have released a new update: UpdraftPlus 1.16.8. We have been hard at work on the latest developments, with our main aim being to fix the issue of a potential rapidly repeating loop that could occur if requested </span><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftclone/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">UpdraftClone</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> credentials were not ready. </span></p>\n<p>We hope this new update help improve your experience when using UpdraftPlus.</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The changelog is as follows. We recommend the update for all users.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">FIX: If requesting clone credentials that were not ready, the loop could rapidly repeat instead of waiting the intended time</span></li>\n<li>TWEAK: Some background updates checks (paid versions) that were intended to be suppressed, weren&#8217;t being.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-new-1-16-8-update/\">UpdraftPlus release new 1.16.8 update</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftplus-release-new-1-16-8-update/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"htt